---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="CalcBuild privacy policy — how we collect, use, and protect your information.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
      <p><strong class="text-slate-800">Last updated:</strong> May 2026</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 border-b-2 border-slate-200 pb-2 mb-4 mt-8">Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>CalcBuild does not collect personal information. Our calculators run entirely in your browser. We use Google Analytics to collect anonymous usage data such as page views, time on site, and general geographic location.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 border-b-2 border-slate-200 pb-2 mb-4 mt-8">Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use cookies for analytics purposes through Google Analytics. These cookies help us understand how visitors interact with our site. You can disable cookies in your browser settings.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 border-b-2 border-slate-200 pb-2 mb-4 mt-8">Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We use Google AdSense to display advertisements. Google may use cookies to serve ads based on your prior visits to our website or other websites.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-800 border-b-2 border-slate-200 pb-2 mb-4 mt-8">Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at our <a href="/contact/" class="text-primary-500 hover:text-primary-600 underline">contact page</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
